go to our open forum and post your questions. Not to brag but we do Hate with precision. We are like a machine up there. Also perhaps you could guest with us sometime? We could take you along and show you the ropes...pointers on what to do right, how to get your pull teams working, etc etc.<br>
<br>
We call our system the lawn mower. We usually have multiple mobs mezzed and &quot;on deck&quot; while we are dispatching our current one. You also need to know which monsters take priority etc etc, like spite golems which are almost 100% MR and un-mezzable. <br>
<br>
Send me a tell in game and post over on our open forums board.<br>
